  "description": "Smoked mackerel is rich and salty, so needs the freshness of apple, cucumber and apple cider vinegar to counterbalance it. Here, we've tumbled it through protein-rich lentils and a dill yoghurt for a flavoursome and healthy mid-week omega-3 fix.",
